---aura_Lucky Reload---
Type :: Buff
Duration :: -1
Icon ::
Max Stacks :: 1
Time Per Tick :: 1.0
Definitions :: [[Custom:LuckyReload]]

---spike_Lucky Reload---
Slot :: Gun
Auras :: [[Lucky Reload]]
Rarity :: Uncommon

Random chance to have reload take half the usual time.

---script_LuckyReload_ReloadWeapon---
rand := import("rand")

if rand.float() < 0.50 && auraAbilityId == abilityId {
    reloadTime = reloadTime * 0.5
}